    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The things I like the most in the my college is Auditorium which is very big in the size and is there largest auditorium in the Haryana one of the largest auditorium",
          "name": "Shubham",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Course affordability of courses college provide is need of middle class students",
          "name": "Aniket",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Easy exams. Yes the level of exams here is not hard. Anyone can pass if he or she study.",
          "name": "Aniket",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers teachimg method is good . Some teacher focus on practical things while other totaly on theory",
          "name": "Abhishek",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is a big ground have trees on its boundaries and have a football ground",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Best library, canteen facilities and also any fest organise for students entertainment purposes.",
          "name": "Bhumika",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "One of most big thing i liked in this college that fees structure . Here is very low fees for every course",
          "name": "Kapil",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are both NCC Army and NCC Air Wing here.",
          "name": "Aashish kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Placements opportunities are very low, if there is it provided only around 3 to 4 lakh highest package.",
