          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Washroom are at bad comdition even girls washroom condition is very bad . Cleaning staff doesn't clean properly",
          "name": "Abhishek",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Only NCC tours go here, not other students.",
          "name": "Aashish kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The other things are dislike most is the lack of sports facility",
          "name": "Shubham",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The other things I dislike the most is there there is no hotel availability in the",
